{"type":null,"faqId":9596,"title":"荣耀X1（7D-501u）7.0  如何使用闪光灯和自动对焦功能？","answer":"<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30047\" /> \n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">在荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">电量过低时，拍照功能将无法使用。清避免在荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">电量过低时拍照。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的闪光灯默认为</span>&nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30052\" width=\"21\" /></span><span><span><span>&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">自动模式，即当周围环境光线较弱时，荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">会自动开开启闪光灯。您也可以在相机取景界面点击此图标，在闪光灯的</span>&nbsp;</span><span><span><span>&nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30054\" /></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">开启模式、<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30053\" /></span></span><span><b><span></span></b><span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">关闭模式、<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30058\" /></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">自动模式间切换。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在相机取景界面中点击需要拍摄的对象，荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">会为您自动对焦。</span></span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":167,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"191","faqTypeCode":"Tablet-Camera-Picture","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1396257786000,"seriesProductName":"7D-501u","visitedTimes":442,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList